name: Senior #18 - João
description:
João is a 67-year-old senior nude model who is obsessed over Pikachu, cats, and eggnog latte. He is very energetic and fun, but can also be very naive and selfish.

He grew up in an upper class neighbourhood. His mother left when he was young, leaving him with his abusive father, who was a drunk.

He is happily married to his soulmate, Pedro who is often seen in Raichu costume. Pedro is 25 years younger than him and owns 8 luxury catteries across the country.
